   Official complaint</span><hr size=1> Hello My Dear Friends in Code of Honor<br>
<br>
I come to you today on a rather unhappy note, Today in the Great Divide I experienced a act rather unbecomeing of Code of honor, and HECK.  <br>
<br>
I was Leveling My wizard at the Kodiak caves there, he is a level 34 gnome named agabaga.  I was camping theese caves for around 2 hours.  A group of Code then showed up at my camp and began to pull mobs from my cave. Now of course I am just one low level wizzy and as I cannot even come close to killing the number of kodiaks in this cave I happily shared them and voiced no complaint. <br>
<br>
This group consided of, Stannleyy, Benas, and Athenya whom I assume was attemtping to help her guildmates level as she is level 49 and would recive no exp from theese mobs. Anyhow I was going about my bussniess pulling, In theese kodiak caves as you may or may not know the pathing is very bugy, if you pull one from around a corner and run out of the cave about 90% of the time bug and pop on top of you. Now this is fine for a group, but for a soloing low hp caster haveing a mob just pop on you unxhe epectedly can kill you. So as such i choose to root and snare them inside the cave and either kill them inside or slowly control the pull while they are snared to the outside of the cave. <br>
<br>
After about 10 or 15 minutes of the Code group being there I recived a tell from 49 druid Athenya asking me to move out of there pulling path, I then pointed out that I had been there for over 2 hours and did not wish to move, she then proceded to acuse me of future complaints about me being trained etc etc that I would not have voiced, I have played here for 3 years, 1 of thoose years as a member of this fine alliance. I knew the risks and was willing to accept them. But none the less she kept voiceing her opinion via tell. <br>
<br>
Now as this char is mainly a pvp char I decided that I would resolve this situation the best way this char knew how, I would simpley kill the 2 people she was helping level. So I went about my bussniess and engaged the 2 lower level code, They fought quite honorably to the best of there ability and fairly, I ended up wining in the end.  Now at this point I sent Athenya a tell reliveing her of all concerns about my saftey informing her that I had killed her to comrads and the pulling issue would no longer be a problem.  I was all ready to compliment her on the fact that she did not OOR heal the younger members. That was untill she began to threaten me, she proceeded to tell me that If I stayed here I would be one sorry little gnome implying that she was going to kill me. Now as i am 34 and she was 49 this was no concern of mine.<br>
<br>
Anyhow at this point the ever so brave level 49 druid challenged me to a duel. Being that I am level 34 I told her that it would be unfair and I did not wish to participate. She then beagan to /tell me with insulting coments and slander. Anyhow i was uphappy with this already.<br>
<br>
now after that I was then medding up outside the kodiak caves at the rock in front when she says I think Ill just pull right here, so about 30 seconds later I was takeing dmg up the wazzzuuu, she has trained 3 kodiaks on me inntentionally.<br>
<br>
I know that Code of Honor does not condone training people, trash talking or just in general acts like this.  I dont wish a fine guild such as yourselfs to have the name, and respect that your guild and its members have come to earn be ruined by such players. Thank you for your time <p><p align=center>
R.I.P Shandralynne Morningdove you are in our all hearts forever 

